<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="lo">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="ແຜງຄວບຄຸມແອດມິນ - ລົດມືສອງ">
    <title>ແຜງຄວບຄຸມແອດມິນ</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+Lao:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-primary">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/admin/dashboard">
                <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="Logo" style="height: 60px; margin-right: 10px;">
                ແຜງຄວບຄຸມແອດມິນ
            </a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav" aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <div class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
                    <a class="nav-link active" href="/admin/dashboard">ແຜງຄວບຄຸມ</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/admin/manage-car">ຈັດການລົດ</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/admin/add-car">ເພີ່ມລົດ</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/admin/manage-sell-requests">ຈັດການຄຳຂໍຂາຍ</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/admin/logout">ອອກຈາກລະບົບ</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container mt-4">
        <h1 class="text-center">ແຜງຄວບຄຸມແອດມິນ</h1>
        <div class="row mt-4">
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
                <div class="card bg-dark text-light">
                    <div class="card-body text-center">
                        <h5 class="card-title">ຈຳນວນລົດທັງໝົດ</h5>
                        <p class="display-6"><%- totalCars || 0 %></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
                <div class="card bg-dark text-light">
                    <div class="card-body text-center">
                        <h5 class="card-title">ຄຳຂໍຂາຍທີ່ລໍຖ້າ</h5>
                        <p class="display-6"><%- pendingRequests || 0 %></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
                <div class="card bg-dark text-light">
                    <div class="card-body text-center">
                        <h5 class="card-title">ລົດພຣີມຽມ</h5>
                        <p class="display-6"><%- premiumCars || 0 %></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row mt-4">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <div class="card bg-dark text-light">
                    <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white">
                        <h3>ສະຖິຕິປະເພດລົດ</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-md-3 mb-3">
                                <p><strong>Sedan:</strong> <%- sedanCount || 0 %></p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-3 mb-3">
                                <p><strong>Hatchback:</strong> <%- hatchbackCount || 0 %></p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-3 mb-3">
                                <p><strong>Pickup:</strong> <%- pickupCount || 0 %></p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-3 mb-3">
                                <p><strong>Crossover:</strong> <%- crossoverCount || 0 %></p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-3 mb-3">
                                <p><strong>SUV:</strong> <%- suvCount || 0 %></p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-3 mb-3">
                                <p><strong>PPV:</strong> <%- ppvCount || 0 %></p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-3 mb-3">
                                <p><strong>MPV:</strong> <%- mpvCount || 0 %></p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="footer text-center bg-dark text-light mt-5">
        <div class="container">
            <p>ທີ່ຢູ່: ນະຄອນຫຼວງວຽງຈັນ, ປະເທດລາວ</p>
            <p>ໂທ: +856 20 1234 5678</p>
            <p>ອີເມວ: contact@yourcarwebsite.com</p>
            <p>ຕິດຕາມພວກເຮົາ:
                <a href="https://www.facebook.com/yourpage" target="_blank" class="text-primary mx-2">Facebook</a>
            </p>
            <p>© 2025 Used Car Sales. ສະຫງວນລິຂະສິດ.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>